---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Make Mars Green — AI Robotics Summer Camp | CreatorPort HK"
  description="AI & Robotics Summer Camp for kids 5–12. 3–7 Aug 2026 in Central, Hong Kong. Small group, bilingual, every child takes their rover home."
>

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-badge" data-lang-en>Summer Camp 2026</div>
    <div class="hero-badge" data-lang-de>Sommercamp 2026</div>

    <h1>Make Mars Green</h1>
    <p class="hero-subtitle" data-lang-en>"Mission Mars" AI Robotics Summer Camp</p>
    <p class="hero-subtitle" data-lang-de>"Mission Mars" KI-Robotik Sommercamp</p>

    <div class="hero-facts">
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>📅</span> 3–7 Aug 2026 · Mon–Fri · 9am–12pm</div>
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>👧</span> <span data-lang-en>Ages 5–12 · Small group</span><span data-lang-de>Alter 5–12 · Kleine Gruppe</span></div>
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>📍</span> 19/F Amtel Building, 144-148 Des Voeux Road Central</div>
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>🚇</span> <span data-lang-en>3 min from Sheung Wan MTR (Exit E1 or A1)</span><span data-lang-de>3 Min. von Sheung Wan MTR (Ausgang E1 oder A1)</span></div>
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>🌐</span> <span data-lang-en>Bilingual English/German</span><span data-lang-de>Zweisprachig Englisch/Deutsch</span></div>
      <div class="hero-fact"><span>🤖</span> <span data-lang-en>Every child takes their own rover home</span><span data-lang-de>Jedes Kind nimmt seinen eigenen Rover mit nach Hause</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-price">$3,500 <span>HKD</span></div>

    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary" data-lang-en>Reserve a Spot</a>
      <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary" data-lang-de>Platz reservieren</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85265427963" target="_blank" class="btn btn-whatsapp" data-lang-en>Ask us on WhatsApp</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85265427963" target="_blank" class="btn btn-whatsapp" data-lang-de>Frag uns auf WhatsApp</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== THE MISSION ===== -->
<section class="section" id="mission">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-en>The Mission</div>
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-de>Die Mission</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-en>Mars needs life. Your child brings it.</h2>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-de>Der Mars braucht Leben. Dein Kind bringt es.</h2>

    <div class="mission-text reveal">
      <p data-lang-en>It's the year 2040. Earth's scientists have discovered that Mars can support plant life — but only if a rover can drill the soil, plant the seeds, and navigate the terrain autonomously. Your child's team has been selected for the mission.</p>
      <p data-lang-de>Das Jahr 2040. Wissenschaftler der Erde haben entdeckt, dass der Mars Pflanzenleben unterstützen kann — aber nur, wenn ein Rover den Boden bohren, Samen pflanzen und das Gelände autonom navigieren kann. Das Team deines Kindes wurde für die Mission ausgewählt.</p>

      <p data-lang-en>Over five days, they'll <strong>design</strong> their rover, <strong>program</strong> its brain, <strong>send an uplink</strong>, <strong>watch</strong> it drive, <strong>learn</strong> from what goes wrong, and <strong>improve</strong> it — just like real engineers at NASA.</p>
      <p data-lang-de>In fünf Tagen werden sie ihren Rover <strong>entwerfen</strong>, sein <strong>Gehirn programmieren</strong>, einen <strong>Uplink senden</strong>, ihn <strong>fahren sehen</strong>, aus Fehlern <strong>lernen</strong> und ihn <strong>verbessern</strong> — genau wie echte Ingenieure bei der NASA.</p>

      <div class="mission-quote" data-lang-en>"Every failed run is data for Mission Control."</div>
      <div class="mission-quote" data-lang-de>"Jede fehlgeschlagene Fahrt sind Daten für die Missionskontrolle."</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== WHAT YOUR CHILD BUILDS & LEARNS ===== -->
<section class="section bg-subtle" id="learns">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-en>What Your Child Builds & Learns</div>
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-de>Was Dein Kind baut & lernt</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-en>From zero to rover in 5 days</h2>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-de>Von null zum Rover in 5 Tagen</h2>

    <div class="learns-grid reveal">
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">🔧</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>Build a real rover</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>Einen echten Rover bauen</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>Motors, gears, gripper arm, drill — assembled by hand</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Motoren, Zahnräder, Greifarm, Bohrer — von Hand zusammengebaut</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">📱</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>Icon-based programming on iPads</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>Icon-basiertes Programmieren auf iPads</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>No typing needed — drag, drop, and run</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Kein Tippen nötig — ziehen, ablegen und ausführen</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">👁️</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>AI camera & sensors</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>KI-Kamera & Sensoren</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>Teach the rover to see and react to its world</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Bringe dem Rover bei zu sehen und auf seine Welt zu reagieren</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">🧠</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>Engineer's mindset</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>Ingenieur-Denkweise</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>Test, fail, learn, improve — the real engineering cycle</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Testen, scheitern, lernen, verbessern — der echte Ingenieurzyklus</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">🤝</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>Teamwork</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>Teamarbeit</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>Collaborate on mission challenges as a crew</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Zusammenarbeit bei Missions-Herausforderungen als Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="learns-item">
        <span class="learns-icon">✅</span>
        <div>
          <strong data-lang-en>Ages 5–12, no experience needed</strong>
          <strong data-lang-de>Alter 5–12, keine Erfahrung nötig</strong>
          <p data-lang-en>We meet every child where they are</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Wir holen jedes Kind dort ab, wo es steht</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TAKE HOME ===== -->
<section class="section" id="takehome">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="takehome-card reveal">
      <div class="takehome-icon">🏠</div>
      <h2 data-lang-en>Take Home</h2>
      <h2 data-lang-de>Zum Mitnehmen</h2>
      <p data-lang-en>Every child takes home their <strong>complete rover</strong> — motors, electronics, and all. Plus tips for continuing to build and program at home.</p>
      <p data-lang-de>Jedes Kind nimmt seinen <strong>kompletten Rover</strong> mit nach Hause — Motoren, Elektronik und alles. Plus Tipps, um zu Hause weiterzubauen und zu programmieren.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== THE 5 DAYS ===== -->
<section class="section bg-subtle" id="schedule">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-en>The 5 Days</div>
    <div class="section-label" data-lang-de>Die 5 Tage</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-en>Mission Plan</h2>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-de>Missionsplan</h2>
    <p class="schedule-note reveal" data-lang-en>Details may vary based on the group's progress</p>
    <p class="schedule-note reveal" data-lang-de>Details können je nach Fortschritt der Gruppe variieren</p>

    <div class="days reveal">
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-num">Day 1</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-en>Mission Briefing</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-de>Missions-Briefing</div>
        <p data-lang-en>Meet your crew. Unbox the rover kit. Learn about Mars. Start building the chassis and wheels.</p>
        <p data-lang-de>Lerne dein Team kennen. Öffne den Rover-Bausatz. Erfahre mehr über den Mars. Beginne mit dem Bau des Chassis und der Räder.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-num">Day 2</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-en>Power Up</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-de>Antrieb starten</div>
        <p data-lang-en>Install motors and gears. Wire the electronics. First driving test — does it move straight?</p>
        <p data-lang-de>Motoren und Zahnräder einbauen. Elektronik verkabeln. Erster Fahrtest — fährt er geradeaus?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-num">Day 3</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-en>Code the Brain</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-de>Das Gehirn programmieren</div>
        <p data-lang-en>Program on iPads using icons. Make the rover follow a path, avoid obstacles, and respond to sensors.</p>
        <p data-lang-de>Programmiere auf iPads mit Icons. Lass den Rover einem Pfad folgen, Hindernisse umfahren und auf Sensoren reagieren.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-num">Day 4</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-en>Mars Tools</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-de>Mars-Werkzeuge</div>
        <p data-lang-en>Add the gripper arm and drill. Train the AI camera to recognize objects. Test autonomous missions.</p>
        <p data-lang-de>Greifarm und Bohrer hinzufügen. KI-Kamera trainieren, um Objekte zu erkennen. Autonome Missionen testen.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="day-card">
        <div class="day-num">Day 5</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-en>Final Mission & Showcase</div>
        <div class="day-title" data-lang-de>Finale Mission & Vorführung</div>
        <p data-lang-en>Complete the "Make Mars Green" challenge. Parents join for the final 30 minutes to watch the rovers in action.</p>
        <p data-lang-de>Schließe die "Make Mars Green"-Challenge ab. Eltern kommen für die letzten 30 Minuten, um die Rover in Aktion zu sehen.</p>
        <div class="day-highlight" data-lang-en>👨‍👩‍👧 Parents' Showcase (final 30 min)</div>
        <div class="day-highlight" data-lang-de>👨‍👩‍👧 Eltern-Vorführung (letzte 30 Min.)</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== TRUST LINE ===== -->
<section class="section" id="trust">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-card reveal">
      <p class="trust-lead" data-lang-en>Led personally by the founder — an <strong>RWTH Aachen-trained engineer</strong>.</p>
      <p class="trust-lead" data-lang-de>Persönlich geleitet vom Gründer — einem <strong>RWTH Aachen-ausgebildeten Ingenieur</strong>.</p>
      <a href="/team" class="trust-link" data-lang-en>Meet Daniel & the team →</a>
      <a href="/team" class="trust-link" data-lang-de>Lerne Daniel & das Team kennen →</a>
      <div class="trust-details">
        <span data-lang-en>Small group with real individual attention</span>
        <span data-lang-de>Kleine Gruppe mit echter individueller Betreuung</span>
        <span> · </span>
        <span data-lang-en>Child-safe materials</span>
        <span data-lang-de>Kindersichere Materialien</span>
        <span> · </span>
        <span data-lang-en>Food-safe plants</span>
        <span data-lang-de>Lebensmittelechte Pflanzen</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== FAQ ===== -->
<section class="section bg-subtle" id="faq">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">FAQ</div>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-en>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-de>Häufig gestellte Fragen</h2>

    <div class="faq-list reveal">
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>Does my child need prior experience?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Braucht mein Kind Vorerfahrung?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>No! The camp is designed for complete beginners aged 5–12. We meet every child where they are and adjust the pace individually.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Nein! Das Camp ist für komplette Anfänger im Alter von 5–12 Jahren konzipiert. Wir holen jedes Kind dort ab, wo es steht, und passen das Tempo individuell an.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>Does my child need to read or type?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Muss mein Kind lesen oder tippen können?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>No. Programming is icon-based on iPads — drag-and-drop, no reading or typing required.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Nein. Die Programmierung ist icon-basiert auf iPads — Drag-and-Drop, kein Lesen oder Tippen erforderlich.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>What does my child take home?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Was nimmt mein Kind mit nach Hause?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>The complete rover including all motors, electronics, and sensors. Plus tips for continuing to build and program at home.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Den kompletten Rover inklusive aller Motoren, Elektronik und Sensoren. Plus Tipps, um zu Hause weiterzubauen und zu programmieren.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>Which language is used during the camp?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>In welcher Sprache findet das Camp statt?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>The camp is led in English. German support is available — Daniel is a native German speaker. We adapt to each child's language comfort.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Das Camp wird auf Englisch geleitet. Deutsche Unterstützung ist verfügbar — Daniel ist deutscher Muttersprachler. Wir passen uns dem Sprachkomfort jedes Kindes an.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>What should my child bring?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Was sollte mein Kind mitbringen?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>Just a water bottle and a small snack. All tools, materials, and iPads are provided by us.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Nur eine Wasserflasche und einen kleinen Snack. Alle Werkzeuge, Materialien und iPads werden von uns gestellt.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>Drop-off and pick-up times?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Bring- und Abholzeiten?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>Drop-off from 8:50am. Camp runs 9:00am–12:00pm. Pick-up by 12:15pm. Day 5 parents join at 11:30am for the showcase.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Bringen ab 8:50 Uhr. Camp läuft 9:00–12:00 Uhr. Abholen bis 12:15 Uhr. Tag 5 kommen Eltern um 11:30 Uhr zur Vorführung.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>Materials & safety?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Materialien & Sicherheit?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en>All materials are provided and child-safe. No hot tools for kids — all soldering is done by the instructor. Food-safe plants are used for the Mars mission. Toilets are on the same floor.</p>
          <p data-lang-de>Alle Materialien werden gestellt und sind kindersicher. Keine heißen Werkzeuge für Kinder — alles Löten wird vom Kursleiter gemacht. Lebensmittelechte Pflanzen werden für die Mars-Mission verwendet. Toiletten sind auf der gleichen Etage.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-q" type="button">
          <span data-lang-en>How can I contact you?</span>
          <span data-lang-de>Wie kann ich euch kontaktieren?</span>
          <span class="faq-chevron">▾</span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p data-lang-en><a href="https://wa.me/85265427963" target="_blank">WhatsApp</a> (fastest) or email <a href="mailto:daniel@creatorport.com.hk">daniel@creatorport.com.hk</a></p>
          <p data-lang-de><a href="https://wa.me/85265427963" target="_blank">WhatsApp</a> (am schnellsten) oder E-Mail an <a href="mailto:daniel@creatorport.com.hk">daniel@creatorport.com.hk</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== STICKY BOTTOM CTA ===== -->
<div class="sticky-cta" id="stickyCta">
  <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary" data-lang-en>Reserve a Spot — $3,500 HKD</a>
  <a href="/checkout" class="btn btn-primary" data-lang-de>Platz reservieren — $3.500 HKD</a>
</div>

</PageLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== HERO ===== */
  .hero {
    padding: 80px 0 48px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--accent);
    background: rgba(15, 110, 86, 0.08);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-facts {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-fact {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .hero-fact span:first-child {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-price {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-price span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  /* ===== MISSION ===== */
  .mission-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .mission-text p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .mission-text strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .mission-quote {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-style: italic;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ===== BG SUBTLE ===== */
  .bg-subtle {
    background: var(--bg-subtle);
  }

  /* ===== LEARNS ===== */
  .learns-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .learns-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .learns-icon {
    font-size: 24px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .learns-item strong {
    font-size: 15px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .learns-item p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ===== TAKE HOME ===== */
  .takehome-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    background: rgba(15, 110, 86, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 110, 86, 0.12);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }

  .takehome-icon {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .takehome-card h2 {
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .takehome-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .takehome-card strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  /* ===== SCHEDULE ===== */
  .schedule-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .days {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .day-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .day-num {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .day-title {
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .day-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .day-highlight {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: rgba(15, 110, 86, 0.06);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  /* ===== TRUST ===== */
  .trust-card {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    background: var(--card-bg);
  }

  .trust-lead {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .trust-lead strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .trust-link {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .trust-link:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .trust-details {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ===== FAQ ===== */
  .faq-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .faq-q {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    font-family: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
    text-align: left;
    cursor: pointer;
    -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;
  }

  .faq-chevron {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-chevron {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
  }

  .faq-a {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .faq-item.open .faq-a {
    max-height: 300px;
  }

  .faq-a p {
    padding: 0 20px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .faq-a a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* ===== STICKY CTA ===== */
  .sticky-cta {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 90;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    padding-bottom: calc(12px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom));
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    transform: translateY(100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .sticky-cta.visible {
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .sticky-cta .btn {
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
  }

  /* ===== DESKTOP ===== */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 100px 0 64px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 42px;
    }

    .hero-facts {
      max-width: 400px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: row;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .hero-actions .btn {
      width: auto;
    }

    .learns-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .days {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .days .day-card:last-child {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .sticky-cta {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // FAQ accordion
  document.querySelectorAll('.faq-q').forEach(function(btn) {
    btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
      var item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
      if (!item) return;
      var wasOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
      // Close all
      document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(function(el) {
        el.classList.remove('open');
      });
      // Toggle current
      if (!wasOpen) item.classList.add('open');
    });
  });

  // Sticky CTA — show when hero scrolls out of view
  var hero = document.querySelector('.hero');
  var stickyCta = document.getElementById('stickyCta');

  if (hero && stickyCta) {
    var observer = new IntersectionObserver(function(entries) {
      entries.forEach(function(entry) {
        stickyCta.classList.toggle('visible', !entry.isIntersecting);
      });
    }, { threshold: 0 });
    observer.observe(hero);
  }
</script>
